- Diffusion of results and training models among the subjects of the macro sectors concerned and vocational training;
- Availability of results and training models for institutions and professionals of the local / regional territories involved;
IN THE LONG TERM:
- Orientation of the public policies of the partners involved on the basis of the results of the project;
- Use of procedures such as a standard model.

